text: Tzernicus also known as Cerminic is a town in Bosnia. Tzernicus is also a titular see of the Roman Catholic ChurchTzernicus at Catholic- Hierarchy.Titular Episcopal See of Tzernicus at GCatholic.org. centered on the ancient city of Cerminic and belonged to the ecclesiastical province of Achrida in Acrida, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==Bishops== *Michael Rusnak (1964.08.25 – 1980.10.13) *Jožef Smej Current ==References== Category:Catholic titular sees in Europe Category:Cities and towns in the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina
